<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>qiú zhǔ yī jiàn shì 迦南31</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ yé sū a! qiú nǐ yī jiàn shì zài zhè xiē rì zi zhōng ná qǐ wǒ lái shǐ yòng
 wǒ yuàn qiān bēi shùn fú huó zài nǐ de zhǐ yì zhōng
 jié wǒ liàn wǒ yòng nǐ de shǒu lái diāo kè wǒ
 kǔn bǎng wǒ làng màn de xīn yīn wǒ zài nǐ shǒu wú fǎ yuè guò
 wǒ yuàn wèi nǐ sǐ wǒ yuàn wèi nǐ huó
 zhǔ yé sū a qiú nǐ lái jiàn chá wǒ qiú nǐ lái shǐ yòng wǒ</lyrics>
